Sentinel v0.9.5.101

Summary:
- Tighten targeted Character ReOCR crop geometry for player names.
- Add position-aware alliance-tag vote extraction inside bracketed tags.
- Reject off-target OCR noise as unresolved instead of ambiguous evidence.
- Add smoke tests for `[PbC]`/`[PBC]` vote selection and noise rejection.
- Update docs and version metadata.

